00:02:58,420 --> 00:03:00,820
 from becoming an absolute blood zone.

75
00:03:00,820 --> 00:03:05,020
 And yet a moment comes where I realize I'm out of my depth.

76
00:03:05,020 --> 00:03:10,020
 And so I do what no self-respecting husband does.

77
