00:03:14,860 --> 00:03:17,220
 and she's explaining to him what's happening in this moment

80
00:03:17,220 --> 00:03:20,100
 that I'm draining the water out,

81
00:03:20,100 --> 00:03:21,820
 that the toilet's continuing to overflow,

82
