00:04:35,740 --> 00:04:37,180
 It was a privation of good.

112
00:04:37,180 --> 00:04:38,460
 It was the absence of good.

113
00:04:38,460 --> 00:04:41,580
 You can go to Eastern religions like Hinduism and Buddhism.

114
00:04:41,580 --> 00:04:42,940
 And what you can learn is that evil

115
