 but it's actually a system of belief

121
00:04:56,660 --> 00:04:59,420
 that many in our world that do not claim faith

122
00:04:59,420 --> 00:05:01,760
 would ascribe to, that there's not just good,

123
00:05:01,760 --> 00:05:02,600
 but there's bad.

124
