00:05:26,820 --> 00:05:30,140
 that results in a negative emotional condition.

139
00:05:30,140 --> 00:05:33,580
 It's where fear and insecurity and trauma come out of.

140
00:05:33,580 --> 00:05:35,540
 That's what everything in the past would say.

141
00:05:35,540 --> 00:05:37,700
 But if you wanted to zoom all the way here to the present

